---
title: Solar entry from IDLE + filled collectors (normal entry)
---
flowchart TD
    A[evaluate called<br/>currentMode = IDLE<br/>collectorsDrained = false]
    A --> B{any sensor stale?<br/>> 150 s since update}
    B -->|yes| Z1[IDLE · sensor_stale]
    B -->|no| C{coldest of outdoor,<br/>collector < 4 °C?}
    C -->|yes| Z2[ACTIVE_DRAIN · freeze_drain<br/>safety override]
    C -->|no| D{collector > tank_bottom + 3?}
    D -->|no| E{greenhouse < 10<br/>AND tank_top ><br/>greenhouse + 5?}
    E -->|yes| F[GREENHOUSE_HEATING · greenhouse_enter]
    E -->|no| G[IDLE · idle]
    D -->|yes| H[Seed peak tracker = tankAvg @ now]
    H --> I[SOLAR_CHARGING · solar_enter<br/>pump ON<br/>vi_btm + vo_coll OPEN<br/>5-min minimum runtime]

    classDef enter fill:#2d4a2d,stroke:#5a9a5a,color:#fff
    classDef idle fill:#333,stroke:#888,color:#ccc
    classDef drain fill:#4a2d2d,stroke:#9a5a5a,color:#fff
    classDef stale fill:#3a3a2d,stroke:#9a9a5a,color:#fff
    class I,F enter
    class G idle
    class Z2 drain
    class Z1 stale
